#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1785
msgid ""
"Manage dictionary TSV imports, whole-site snapshot imports, and exports in "
"one place. TSV rows are grouped by headword so search, browse, bulk "
"translations, and word-linking all use the same data."
msgstr ""
"Verwalte Wörterbuch-TSV-Importe, Gesamtwebsite-Snapshot-Importe und Exporte "
"an einem Ort. TSV-Zeilen sind nach Stichwörtern gruppiert, sodass Suche, "
"Browsen, Massenübersetzungen und Vokabelverknüpfungen dieselben Daten "
"verwenden."

#. translators: %s: URL to the dictionary sources screen
#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1794
msgid ""
"Use the <a href=\"%s\">Dictionary Sources</a> screen to define per-"
"dictionary attribution text, source detail URLs, and default dialect tags "
"before importing rows from a new source."
msgstr ""
"Verwende den Bildschirm <a href=\"%s\">Wörterbuchquellen</a>, um vor dem "
"Import von Zeilen aus einer neuen Quelle den Attributionstext, die URLs der "
"Quellenangaben und die Standard-Dialekt-Tags für jedes Wörterbuch "
"festzulegen."

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1801
msgid "Manage Dictionary Sources"
msgstr "Wörterbuch-Quellen verwalten"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1805
msgid ""
"Whole-site dictionary snapshots preserve stable import keys so you can "
"export the site dictionary, edit it locally, then reimport it in override "
"mode without breaking linked learning words that already point at those "
"dictionary entries."
msgstr ""
"Gesamtwebsite-Wörterbuch-Snapshots bewahren importierte Wörterbucheinträge, "
"mehrsprachige Definitionen, strukturierte Bedeutungen und Verknüpfungen zu "
"Lernvokabeln."

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1809
msgid "Export Whole Dictionary Snapshot"
msgstr "Gesamten Wörterbuch-Snapshot exportieren"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1810
msgid ""
"Exports every LL Tools dictionary entry on this site, plus the dictionary "
"source registry, as a JSON snapshot. Keep each entry's import_key intact "
"when editing so override imports update the existing entry instead of "
"creating a new one."
msgstr ""
"Exportiert jeden LL Tools-Wörterbucheintrag auf dieser Website sowie das "
"Wörterbuch-Quellenregister als JSON-Snapshot. Lasse den import_key jedes "
"Eintrags beim Bearbeiten unverändert, damit Überschreibungsimporte den "
"vorhandenen Eintrag aktualisieren, statt einen neuen zu erstellen."

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1814
msgid "Export Dictionary Snapshot"
msgstr "Wörterbuch-Snapshot exportieren"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1858
msgid "TSV File"
msgstr "TSV Datei"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1862
msgid ""
"Expected columns: entry, definition, gender_number, entry_type, parent, "
"needs_review, page_number. Header-based TSVs can also include source_id, "
"source_dictionary, source_row_idx, raw_headword, title_keys, dialect, "
"dialects, and multilingual gloss columns like definition_full_tr, "
"definition_tr, gloss_tr, translation_en, and definition_full_de."
msgstr ""
"Erwartete Spalten: Eintrag, Definition, gender_number, entry_type, "
"Elternteil, needs_review, page_number. Header-basierte TSVs können auch "
"source_id, source_dictionary, source_row_idx, raw_headword, title_keys, "
"Dialekt, Dialekte und mehrsprachige Glossenspalten wie definition_full_tr, "
"definition_tr, gloss_tr, translation_en und definition_full_de enthalten."

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1865
msgid ""
"Large imports now run in short batches with a live progress bar. Keep this "
"window open while the import is running; if you close it, reopening this "
"screen will let you resume the same job."
msgstr ""
"Große Importe laufen jetzt in kurzen Batches mit einem Live-"
"Fortschrittsbalken. Lass dieses Fenster geöffnet, während der Import läuft; "
"wenn du es schließt, kannst du denselben Job wieder aufnehmen."

