#: templates/vocab-lesson-template.php:445
msgid "Word Set"
msgstr "Vokabelset"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1873
msgid "No word set scope"
msgstr "Kein Vokabelset Umfang"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1881
msgid ""
"Use a word set when this dictionary belongs to one language/course only. "
"Leave it unscoped for combined or pan-dialect dictionaries. Existing "
"headwords are matched within the same import scope."
msgstr ""
"Verwende ein Vokabelset, wenn das Wörterbuch nur zu einer Sprache/einem Kurs"
" gehört. Lasse es für kombinierte oder sprachübergreifende Wörterbücher "
"frei. Vorhandene Stichwörter werden innerhalb desselben Importbereichs "
"abgeglichen."

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1886
msgid "Entry Language"
msgstr "Eintragssprache"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1890
msgid "Definition Language"
msgstr "Definitionssprache"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1894
msgid "Import Options"
msgstr "Import-Optionen"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1898
msgid ""
"Replace existing structured senses for matching headwords instead of "
"merging."
msgstr ""
"Ersetze vorhandene strukturierte Bedeutungen für übereinstimmende "
"Stichwörter, anstatt sie zusammenzuführen."

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1904
msgid "Import Dictionary TSV"
msgstr "Wörterbuch importieren TSV"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1909
msgid "Import Whole Dictionary Snapshot"
msgstr "Gesamten Wörterbuch-Snapshot importieren"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1910
msgid ""
"Upload a JSON snapshot previously exported from LL Tools. Merge mode adds "
"and updates entries from the file. Override mode makes the site dictionary "
"match the file exactly, deleting dictionary entries and source-registry "
"items that are not present in the uploaded snapshot."
msgstr ""
"Lade einen zuvor aus LL Tools exportierten JSON-Snapshot hoch. Der "
"Zusammenführen-Modus fügt Einträge aus der Datei hinzu und aktualisiert sie."
" Der Überschreiben-Modus gleicht das Website-Wörterbuch exakt an die Datei "
"an und löscht Wörterbucheinträge sowie Quellenregisterelemente, die im "
"hochgeladenen Snapshot nicht vorhanden sind."

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1917
msgid "Snapshot File"
msgstr "Snapshot-Datei"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1920
msgid ""
"Use the whole-site JSON snapshot exported from this screen. Large snapshot "
"imports run in the same resumable browser batches as TSV imports."
msgstr ""
"Verwende den JSON-Snapshot der gesamten Site, der von diesem Bildschirm "
"exportiert wird. Große Snapshot-Importe laufen in denselben resumierbaren "
"Browser-Batches wie TSV-Importe."

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1924
msgid "Import Mode"
msgstr "Import-Modus"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1927
msgid "Merge into existing dictionary"
msgstr "In bestehendes Wörterbuch einbinden"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1928
msgid "Override site dictionary from snapshot"
msgstr "Site-Wörterbuch aus Snapshot überschreiben"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1930
msgid ""
"Override mode updates matching entries by import_key, keeps linked learning "
"words attached to those entries, and deletes dictionary entries that are "
"missing from the snapshot."
msgstr ""
"Der Überschreibungsmodus aktualisiert übereinstimmende Einträge anhand von "
"import_key, behält mit diesen Einträgen verknüpfte Lernvokabeln bei und "
"ersetzt nur importierte Wörterbuchdaten."

#: includes/admin/dictionary-import-admin.php:1935
msgid "Import Dictionary Snapshot"
msgstr "Wörterbuch-Snapshot importieren"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-sources-admin.php:24
#: includes/admin/dictionary-sources-admin.php:25
#: includes/admin/dictionary-sources-admin.php:82
msgid "LL Dictionary Sources"
msgstr "LL Wörterbuch-Quellen"

#: includes/admin/dictionary-sources-admin.php:84
msgid ""
"Define reusable source records for imported dictionaries. Each source can "
"carry a short public attribution statement, a public source-information page"
" URL for the dictionary badges, and default dialect tags that are applied "
"when an import row does not provide its own dialect field."
